{"tid":304550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣首間Apple Store開幕　吸引上千人排隊","createTime":"2017-07-01T03:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T04:40:55.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81ecc6b88d5fe8d4bd6bc037ae6cf05334d3e166","tid":304550,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"台灣首間Apple Store今天早上11點在台北101百貨一樓開幕，現揚排隊人潮估有千人，一路排到大馬路上，果粉頂著大太陽，等著擠進台灣首間Apple Store。<br />\n<br />\nApple Store台灣直營店的頭香被美國來的Steve搶走，排了4天，而台灣客頭香是MacUknow網站站長蘋果梗他說：「蘋果對他來說是一種信仰，身邊有一群超資深果粉圈前輩，大家等了十幾年，今天約好一起圓夢，進去後第一件事是想要不疾不徐坐在小椅子上，和昨晚一起排隊的老朋友們閒聊。」可以感受到對於蘋果強烈的信仰。（周淑萍／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170701/420_8e53c7eaa2630ab32360c311d7b86b51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170701%2F420_8e53c7eaa2630ab32360c311d7b86b51.jpg&h=08faced0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb8d6388d4fe53e2539f195ca8373c98c3780df","tid":304550,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"咁大個台灣先得一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc603ea3ead3f03642676cc9a4bae514e4ad283","tid":304550,"uid":64699,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:52:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de61cae914ab49c506d0f517adaa0718825a13b8","tid":304550,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁大個台灣先得一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地香港人個個都有錢有車有樓<br />\n蘋果先開咁多間係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d5dae59695e556a24164852e7986970fdaf927","tid":304550,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-